    <item>
      <title>Meta 将利用面部识别技术打击假冒名人诈骗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/meta-to-use-facial-recognition-to-fight-fake-celebrity-scams</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Facebook 母公司 Meta Platforms Inc. 将开始使用面部识别技术打击利用名人照片使其看起来更合法的诈骗行为，这种策略被称为“名人诱饵广告”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/meta-to-use-facial-recognition-to-fight-fake-celebrity-scams</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克因在 Robotaxi 发布会上使用“银翼杀手”图像而被起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/musk-accused-of-blade-runner-copyright-infringement-on-robotaxi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[好莱坞电影制片人 Alcon Entertainment 起诉埃隆·马斯克，称特斯拉公司在最近的一次活动中使用了受 2017 年电影《银翼杀手 2049》启发的图像，尽管该电影的许可已被拒绝。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/musk-accused-of-blade-runner-copyright-infringement-on-robotaxi</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 20:34:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>软件巨头 SAP 利用人工智能吸引客户，云销售额大幅增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/sap-cloud-revenue-rises-25-in-quarter-as-legacy-clients-switch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲最大的软件公司 SAP SE 致力于通过人工智能工具和分析将客户从本地运行的系统转移，其云计算收入在第三季度增长了 25%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/sap-cloud-revenue-rises-25-in-quarter-as-legacy-clients-switch</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 20:10:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SEC 将加强对经纪商和顾问使用的人工智能工具的审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/sec-examiners-will-zoom-in-on-ai-tools-used-by-brokers-advisers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国证券交易委员会的审查人员明年将加强对金融公司使用人工智能的审查，这是监管机构对新兴技术日益担忧的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/sec-examiners-will-zoom-in-on-ai-tools-used-by-brokers-advisers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 20:01:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CFA 协会研究人工智能对考试和课程的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/cfa-institute-researches-ai-s-impact-on-testing-and-curriculum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[负责管理特许金融分析师认证的 CFA 协会正在研究人工智能如何改进其产品和考试，目前平均通过率约为 50%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/cfa-institute-researches-ai-s-impact-on-testing-and-curriculum</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 19:26:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
